metadata.title: RA Family: Quick FSP 4.6.0 Labs: Introduction to FSP using Blinky

sections.content: This Quick FSP Lab will take you through the process of:

This process will test out the complete RA FSP environment and will make it easy to start your own development project. We recommend you continue with a few follow-on Quick FSP Labs. A link to the list of labs in the series is always given at the end of each of these Quick Labs articles.
The below attached PDFs contain the guide for this Quick FSP Lab- either for the EK-RA6M3 or EK-RA6M4. Simply download and follow along to complete this lab.
The list of Quick FSP Labs is available here.
